author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Tile floor doorway tips…I used a scrap piece of DITRA and tile to undercut the door casing/jamb. The DITRA is 1/8-inch thick. That’s roughly the same thickness of my thin-set mortar. The tile fit like a glove. If you’re tiling a bathroom check out our Video Library at homerepairtutor.com 👍🏽🔥#tile #tilefloor #bathroomgoals #newyearsresolution
title: Tile Floor Doorway Tips - #shorts #homerepairtutor
